	* cc-mode.texi:   Added ACM to the list of authors.
	  Renamed "Other Electric Commands" to "Electric Keys and Keywords"
	  In "Electric Keys and Keywords", added descriptions of {, }, :, ;, ,,,
	    and tidied up the wording a bit.
