	* cc-mode.el: fixed docstring for c++-tab-always-indent

Wed Jul 29 14:50:46 1992  Barry A. Warsaw, ITB  (warsaw@anthem)

	* cc-mode.el:
	this branch combines C and C++ modes for inclusion into emacs 19

